[End of game results modifiers\Distance Walked]
author=bungholio
description=The values need to be that pesky 32bit floating point decimal format.
So these are some values.
0 - 0
1 - 3f800000
2 - 40000000
5 - 40a00000
10 - 41200000
100 - 42c80000
500 - 43fa0000
1000 - 447a0000
1000000 - 49742400 (might need this for distance walked)

I tried all the codes without a joker command with the value for 100, and all of them appeared as 100, except distance walked was 0.10Km and total time and flashlight times were 0:01:40.
patch=1,EE,206BF9B8,extended,49742400

